{"data":[{"id":"1782269020449457","contents":"사용자 관리\r\n======\r\n예시\r\n------\r\n서로 다른 쉘 세션을 열어 수행함\r\n\r\n- SYS 계정으로 수행","height":160,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1782269063455515","contents":"create user user1 identified by 'user1';    --user1 계정 생성\r\ndrop user user1;                            --user1 계정 삭제 \r\ncreate user mach1 identified by 'mach1';    --mach1 계정 생성\r\ncreate user mach2 identified by 'mach2';    --mach2 계정 생성","height":99,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":false,"type":"sql","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true,"brief":true},{"id":"1782269083134757","contents":"show users;","height":38,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":false,"type":"shell","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1782269105350258","contents":"alter user mach2 identified by 'mach22';            -- mach2의 패스워드 변경\r\n\r\ncreate table mach (id integer, name varchar(20));   --mach라는 이름의 테이블을 생성\r\ncreate index mach_id_idx on mach(id);               --mach테이블에 인덱스 생성\r\n\r\ninsert into mach values(1, 'Alex');                 --mach테이블에 데이터 입력\r\ninsert into mach values(2, 'Brown');\r\ninsert into mach values(3, 'Charley');\r\n\r\nselect * from mach;                                 --mach테이블의 데이터 조회\r\n\r\ndrop user SYS;                                      --SYS 계정 삭제 시도  오류 발생함","height":249,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":false,"type":"sql","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true,"brief":true},{"id":"1782269168224754","contents":"- mach1 계정으로 접속\r\n```sql\r\nconnect mach1/mach1;\r\n\r\nalter user mach2 identified by 'mach2222';\r\n\r\nalter user mach1 identified by mach11;\r\n```","height":173,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1782269207484426","contents":"- mach1 계정으로 다시 접속 (비번 변경 후)\r\n```sql\r\nconnect mach1/mach11;\r\n\r\ncreate table mach (id integer, name varchar(20));\r\n\r\ncreate index mach_id_idx on mach(id);\r\n\r\ninsert into mach values(4, 'Dennis');\r\n\r\ninsert into mach values(5, 'Eric');\r\n\r\ninsert into mach values(6, 'Frank');\r\n\r\nselect * from mach;\r\n```","height":200,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1782269339365738","contents":"- 다시 sys 계정으로 접속\r\n```sql\r\nselect * from mach;\r\n\r\nselect * from mach1.mach;\r\n\r\ngrant select on mach to mach2;\r\n\r\ndrop user mach1; -- mach1계정으로 만든 테이블이 존재하므로 삭제할 수 없음\r\n\r\nconnect mach2/mach22;\r\n\r\nselect * from sys.mach;\r\n```","height":280,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1782270292298680","contents":"- 다시 mach1 계정으로 접속\r\n```sql\r\nconnect mach1/mach11;\r\n\r\ndrop table mach;\r\n\r\nconnect SYS/MANAGER;\r\n\r\ndrop user mach1;\r\n\r\ndrop user mach2;\r\n\r\nshow users;\r\n\r\ndrop table mach;\r\n```","height":325,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true}]}